Purpose
This file groups the runtime dependencies that agents need during execution.

Linear intent
1. Define the runtime services record as the loaded runtime config plus the initialized AegisLM-backed LLM client.
2. Provide `create` so production code can build the services directly from the runtime config.
3. Return an explicit error when the LLM client cannot be created.
4. Provide `of_llm_client` so tests and advanced callers can inject a custom client while keeping the same service shape.

